{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "NewsArticle", "headline": "Deandre Ayton 會在太陽隊得到他想要的頂級合約嗎？", "author": {"@type": "Person", "name": "Bas客Ball", "url": "https://basketball.fanpiece.com/BaskBall/"}, "datePublished": "2022-11-03", "publisher": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "FanPiece", "logo": {"@type": "ImageObject", "url": "/images/fanpiece-logo-white.png"}}, "articleSection": "NBA", "articleBody": "當太陽隊在賽季前未能與 2018 年選秀狀元 Deandre Ayton 達成頂薪續約，這讓整個聯盟的所有人都感到驚訝，Deandre Ayton 除了幫助太陽隊打進總冠軍賽之外，2018 年選秀梯次的 Luka Doncic、Trae Young、Shai Gilgeous-Alexander、Michael Porter Jr. 等人都已經與球隊續約。從談判一開始雙方就互不相讓，Deandre Ayton 想與球隊簽下五年的合約，不過球隊只願意簽四年，因此雙方才能未達成協議。", "image": ["/images/loading.svg?v=202101"], "keywords": "NBA, Phoenix Suns, Deandre Ayton, Chris Paul, Devin Booker", "url": "https://basketball.fanpiece.com/BaskBall/Deandre-Ayton-%E6%9C%83%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD%E9%9A%8A%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E4%BB%96%E6%83%B3%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E9%A0%82%E7%B4%9A%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E5%97%8E-c1418767.html"}